## Implementation Order

1. Phase 1 first — get the core engine working with tests.
2. Phase 2 — computed attributes (smaller integration surface, lower risk).
3. Phase 3 — playbook steps (richer context, more complex result handling).
4. Phase 4 — hardening (can be done incrementally alongside 2 and 3).
